original_title: Brooklyn: Old Mill Road - Fountain Avenue
text:
Old Mill Road, south side, east of Fountain Ave. to Crescent (background) Street, showing also at a point beyond Crescent Street where one Old Mill Road meets the one in this view forming a right angle prior to its continuance southward to the "Red Mill" which is no longer in existence. July 5, 1934.

P. L. Sperr.
